text: Ouareau may refer to: * Camp Ouareau, a vacation camp, in Notre-Dame-de-la- Merci, Quebec, Canada * Lake Ouareau, in municipality of Saint-Donat, Quebec, Canada * Ouareau River, Saint-Paul, Quebec, Canada * Forêt-Ouareau Regional Park, a regional park in Matawinie, Lanaudière, Quebec, Canada
title: Ouareau
